title: Toyoko Oku
text: Toyoko Oku (born 14 June 1966) is a Japanese <a href="archery">archer</a>. She competed in the women's <a href="Archery%20at%20the%201988%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20individual">individual</a> and <a href="Archery%20at%20the%201988%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20team">team</a> events at the <a href="1988%20Summer%20Olympics">1988 Summer Olympics</a>.
